---
title: Sticky BBQ Chicken with wedges and garlicky broccoli
description: Garlicky broccoli and crispy wedges accompany sweet and savoury BBQ chicken in this dish the whole household is sure to enjoy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R15_W18_IE_IEXCLC0095-3_Main_high-80c611ae.jpg
